    <body>
        <p>When you want to use styles in your content, the stylesheet needs to be made available for the content in question. In <MadCap:variable name="Products.Flare" />, you can associate regular stylesheets with a single topic<MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.FlareOnlineOnly,FlareGuides.FlareStylesGuide"> (see <MadCap:xref href="../../../Styles/Applying_Style_Sheets_to_Topics.htm">Applying Stylesheets to Topics</MadCap:xref>)</MadCap:conditionalText>. However, you also have the option of using a regular stylesheet as a "master," applying it at either the project or target level, or both.</p>
